description:
This market will resolve to “Yes” if any Binance 1 minute DOGE/USDT candle titled with a date between 2022/10/31 0:01 through 2022/11/30 12:00 (inclusive) in the ET timezone has a final “Low” price of 0.09999 or lower. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No". 

The final relevant candle for this market will be the 1 minute DOGE/USDT candle titled "2022/11/30 12:00" in the ET timezone. The resolution source for this market is https://www.binance.com, specifically the DOGE/USDT “Low” prices currently available at https://www.binance.com/en/trade/DOGE_USDT?_from=markets&theme=dark&type=spot with “1m” and “Original” selected on the top bar. To see the “Low” prices, mouse over particular candles and look at the value after “Low: ” at the top of the chart.

The API url https://api.binance.com/api/v3/klines?symbol=DOGEUSDT&interval=1m with relevant startDate and endDate parameters may be used in the event that the chart is unavailable. Please note that this market is about the price according to Binance DOGE/USDT, not the price according to other sources or spot markets.
